Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎麼那麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都說了是被奇怪的傢伙給纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很正常地在走著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你別跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會讓你逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  你快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  就剩一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經查到佐天同學手機的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  先讓我把臂章…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  就因為你跑得太快才會摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,332)\fs16\fsp0}Judgement
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以故意傷害未遂的嫌疑逮捕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}風紀委員？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}喂  她是能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看見空間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是能力者  只要我們全部圍上去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不知天高地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我想怎麼那麼久還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是她們的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢多管閒事  就先拿你開刀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然店就要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  他們到底是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都解決掉了才來問這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總人口230萬人  其中的80%是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們每天都在這個學園都市裡努力培養和提高能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在其頂點的7名超能力者的第三位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,332)\fs16\fsp1}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超電磁炮  御阪美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,332)\fs16\fsp2}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說姐姐大人  你到底有那份覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼覺悟？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼覺悟的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的能力在被人仰慕的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是被人嫉妒的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是像昨天那種輕率的行為引起別人注意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想要暗算和利用的人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  幹嘛無視我只顧回短信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學發來的  說是已經離開宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你也趕快把工作做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是超帥氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怎麼說來著  就是所謂的秒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅一招就把那些不良少年全部打趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你隨便抄近路才會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學  馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帖  請帖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣矇混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼今天要把見面地點定在御阪學姐她們的學校裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  御阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  婚後同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有灣內同學和泡浮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究課題用的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校也真的  暑假課題多得數不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯  光是選資料就要費不少力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天御阪學姐也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在到約定時間之前打發一下時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課題我都已經搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只要想的話  半天就能搞定這堆東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  婚後同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀不好  我怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  婚後學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是食蜂學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著屬於她派系的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是超能力者的第五位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為這所學校的女王還真是名符其實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我總覺得沒辦法喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼會這樣  這絕不是在背後說她壞話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館內禁止竊竊私語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  明明剛才和別人聊了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你不願跟我聊天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便亂碰別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  真嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是給某位男士的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來挑釁的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢  一對一的話我很難贏你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪同學完全不受我的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難對付啊  電磁屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是御阪學姐和食蜂學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個人怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  雖然一對一我很難贏你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讓這麼多的常盤台學生來做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是很棘手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼站起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是御阪學姐和食蜂學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}我先走了  女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往的特別下流的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市最強的精神系能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理掌握  食蜂操祈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(281,332)\fs16\fsp0}MentalOut
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別露出那麼嚇人的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是警告  最近你好像多了很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你侵入了我的勢力範圍  我是不會讓你好過的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是問個問題的話  請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是中學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢  至少表面上是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我的篡改能力  我說什麼就是什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春她們已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然就空間移動過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？白井同學怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是日常的感情交流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啊  春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地讓你到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  我非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還買了很多好吃的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡聚集了很多學園都市裡特別有名的店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春可是很期待給春上同學介紹這些店的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為這裡真是非常棒的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管怎麼說  這典雅的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣中都充滿著玫瑰的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你今天才配合這種氛圍的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼配合啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎麼會知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才初春在選蛋糕的時候就偷偷地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多玫瑰非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連春上同學也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你沒反應的話果然感覺不夠勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  別在這裡爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來探望病人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請在這裡填寫上必要項目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是熟門熟路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黃泉川老師和鐵裝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們今天來幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來探望病人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  老師們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發生什麼事件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  和我們幹過架的冒牌過激派的一員在這裡接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在總算是恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要將他轉移至警備員附屬醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好教育他們一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請適可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌過激派？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這座城市裡還是有著很多問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃哦  衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  剛才在店裡和初春同學一起吃了自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人大概吃了二十個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像恢復得很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過康復訓練就有些辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都來探望我了  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  快點康復成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期開始一起上同一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們渴不渴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點呢  我們去買點果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢  那麼春上同學  我們先失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,們？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就回來  你們隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（俺妹第一卷注目）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  到底是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這待會兒再說  先去買果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…康復訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枝先同學也在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚喜…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  那個禮物光就這麼交給她我覺得衝擊力不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這種事情氣氛很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是藏在蛋糕當中之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者香檳的杯底之類的也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過再怎麼樣也沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底哪些是認真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  就用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為「什麼啊  只是束花啊  但裡面其實是」作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  那我去買花了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的姐姐大人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是御阪學姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這下搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要心意到了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子  我需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  姐姐大人  請稍微冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明都已經聯繫我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦個轉移手續要多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  看守的人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的人給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火災？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵裝  聯絡下面的人讓他們進行緊急配置  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才緊急報警鈴啟動…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們姑且去確認一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人和佐天同學先去枝先同學那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼  請都不要再做出和昨天一樣的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了  是不是發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到哪裡都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市全域的緊急配置已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來  否則這小鬼的腦袋就要被打飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備轉移的犯人逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉川隊長正在追捕  全員也在集中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不節外生枝  你們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  黑子到底把我當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在擔心你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為御阪學姐淨是做些危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那才是御阪學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就那樣安排…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要隨便刺激他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉川老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌過激派把屋頂封鎖以後躲在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也快點去安全的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枝先同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領衣  領衣  她一直都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的朋友被當做人質了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那個  領衣她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  御阪學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  出發  起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  再加大點馬力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有加啊  但沒法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  是這傢伙的同伴麼  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明都那樣提醒過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是沒辦法的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學沒事吧  有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓人擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐的包包…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  御阪學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總體來說還算順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那小鬼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到小鬼  剛才那能力者真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所謂的「電擊使」麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,332)\fs16\fsp0}ElectroMaster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那身制服  難道說是常盤台的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個名門校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  常盤台的電擊使的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(355,332)\fs15\fsp-1}ElectroMaster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了  常盤台的電擊使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,332)\fs15\fsp-1}ElectroMaster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個都市最強的發電能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力者的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(313,332)\fs16\fsp2}Level5
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超電磁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,332)\fs16\fsp2}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  冒牌過激派先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是一如既往的御阪學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那才是御阪學姐的優點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  枝先同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是制服  絆理的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能早日穿上這個  請加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大家昨天一起去買的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  枝先同學  其實我原本還準備了更加棒的驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為前面發生了不少事  商店都關門了  於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經夠吃驚了  而且還很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:22:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這座學園都市真是永遠都不會讓人感到無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐還是一如既往的帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學也平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春也春光乍洩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下星期會是什麼顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要掀我的裙子




